event.title: inhabited the county from the 1st century BC

data.event: A Brythonic tribe, the Iceni, inhabited the county from the 1st century BC to the end of the 1st century AD.
The Iceni revolted against the Roman invasion in 47 AD, and again in 60 AD led by Boudica.
